    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063390/extras/a56487e9e801d0bc31c5ae6ce856f313.webp?t=1763044823\" width=612 height=57 /></span>Crash land Fantasy is a 2D Action Adventure Story Game made with the Ren.py Visual Novel Engine.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It's a cinematic experience with fun cute characters, engaging visuals and an interactive story with multiple endings.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063390/extras/3b460a84e5e60a66cade552b71991f72.avif?t=1763044823\" width=582 height=298 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063390/extras/cfdddde99b3106bc4d95a8116a760f89.webp?t=1763044823\" width=612 height=57 /></span>In the space fairing future a research satellite orbits above a planet unestablished by the federation, One of the few remaining who's natives possess the ability to use what's known as Magic. Of course you don't believe in 'Magic' your scientists after all but after many years gaining no real understanding of the phenomenon the research project gets shut down.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You worry what you'll do with your life next but suddenly the satellite gets knocked out of orbit by a mysterious magic force causing the remaining two inhabitants of the craft to Crash Land on the fantasy planet. You and your android captain must try to survive on this planet which is ruled by nature.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Go on a fun action adventure and meet friends along the way, Figure out the mystery behind the magical force that made you crash as you try to get back home! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063390/extras/bcaee440fa95fe055faaf91dbd2763c8.webp?t=1763044823\" width=612 height=57 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063390/extras/c8b297fb481308cc6fbfafdb0e56aa2a.avif?t=1763044823\" width=560 height=452 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063390/extras/944f773d5287e53095e1b25c0cf45751.avif?t=1763044823\" width=560 height=392 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063390/extras/97f04fe65748af7803e493859a58001b.avif?t=1763044823\" width=560 height=384 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063390/extras/4540755fa78a9a9d7efe7641c7e94073.avif?t=1763044823\" width=560 height=399 /></span></p>",
